    "description": {
      "zh": "FORT OK“Defender-2”单兵防护装备是 FORT 公司生产的另一款知名防弹衣“Defender”的改进型号，为要员保护任务以及作战部队的行动需求进行了优化。该装备围绕防弹插板设计，最大限度提升了模块化能力。",
      "en": "The FORT OK \"Defender-2\" operational kit is a modification of the popular body armor FORT \"Defender\" designed for both VIP and for employees of operational combat units. The kit uses the maximum capabilities of the modular principle of building armor based on steel plates."
